metadata.description:
The best email I’ve ever seen as a leader? It came from Larry Page — 4 days after becoming CEO again.

In one message, he told 19,000 people: change is coming.
Clear. No buzzwords. No confusion. And it worked — 95% of the shift happened in 20 days.

In this clip, I explain the two biggest lessons from that moment:
- Make it clear that change is inevitable.
- Be radically transparent — or just say “I can’t answer that.”

If you’re a leader, you don’t have to have all the answers. But you do have to tell the truth.

#MoGawdat #LarryPage #Leadership #ChangeManagement #Transparency #GoogleX #CorporateTruth #OrganizationalChange #NoBuzzwords #RealLeadership
